     $salt = 'fs';
     $pass = 'heynow';
     $out = crypt($salt, $pass);
     print "$out\n"; 
returns this:
bash-2.03$ perl test3.pl
$1$heynow$0jPK61iCt92vyGs2ciUUa.

I do not know the cause of this, or how it can be fixed, it seems to be dependent on this particular machine.
